t,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hiding-place, of a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wild"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bull,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which he makes for himself at the foot of the kind of tree called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroTFY","text_ar":"اَرْطًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (TA:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abohaA='N","text_ar":"اَبْهَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buhuw~N","text_ar":"بُهُوٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [quasi-pl.-n.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bahiY~N","text_ar":"بَهِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b5-  Any"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vacant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intervening, space."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interior of the chest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) of a man and of any beast: (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"space that intervenes between the two breasts and the uppermost part of the chest"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bahowu AlS~adori","text_ar":"بَهْوُ الصَّدْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part between"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"within"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the extremities of the ribs that project over the belly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and in her that is pregnant, (JK, K,) whatever she be, (JK,) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resting-place of the fœtus, between the two haunches:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abohaA='N","text_ar":"اَبْهَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abohK","text_ar":"اَب